  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine choice of anticoagulant therapy during acute and
      chronic stages of ischemic stroke/TIA and short- and long-term outcomes, including stroke
      recurrence and bleeding complications, in patients having nonvalvular atrial fibrillation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
